name: Cash Me Outside - How Bout Dat Adventure
name_original: Cash Me Outside - How Bout Dat Adventure
description:
Cash Me Outside - How Bout Dat Adventure is a FREE platformer adventure game!

Luckily Dr Phil ain't here!

Find the key to unlock next level, avoid enemies and obstacles and find your way out!

Get through all 24 rooms to complete the game - but be careful - it is not as easy as it looks!

Get bonus points by collecting coins. Get ranked in leaderboard.

Entertaining gameplay, hours of fun guaranteed!

Cash Me Outside - How Bout Dat Adventure is waiting for you - download now and share with friends!

How bow dat?
